{% doc %}
  Renders the body of a "Details, Materials & Care" accordion tab.

  For the auto content sources (dimensions / delivery / care / customization) it
  renders a rich, brand-consistent layout that is authored once and reused for
  every product. "dimensions" additionally lists the product's own Size option
  values (mirroring the variant picker). Any other source falls back to the
  block's own rich-text content, or the product description.

  @param {block} block - The accordion block (content_source / content / use_product_description)
  @param {product} product - The current product (for description and Size options)

  @example
  {% render 'product-detail-tab-content', block: block, product: product %}
{% enddoc %}

{%- liquid
  assign source = block.settings.content_source | default: 'custom'
-%}

{%- case source -%}
  {%- when 'dimensions' -%}
    {%- assign size_option = null -%}
    {%- for opt in product.options_with_values -%}
      {%- assign opt_name = opt.name | downcase -%}
      {%- if opt_name contains 'size' -%}
        {%- assign size_option = opt -%}
        {%- break -%}
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
    <div class="dm-desc">
      <div class="dm-desc__intro">
        <p class="dm-desc__eyebrow">Dimensions &amp; sizing</p>
        <p>Every WRYDECO piece is crafted to order in the sizes shown here. Choose the option that best suits your space — and because each piece is handmade, dimensions can be tailored to fit exactly where it will live.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__block">
        <h4>Available sizes</h4>
        {%- if size_option and size_option.values.size > 0 -%}
          <p>Pick your size for this piece from the options below (matching the Size selector above):</p>
          <div class="dm-desc__chips">
            {%- for val in size_option.values -%}
              {%- assign val_clean = val | strip -%}
              {%- if val_clean != blank and val_clean != 'Custom' -%}
                <span class="dm-desc__chip">{{ val_clean | escape }}</span>
              {%- endif -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
        {%- else -%}
          <p>This piece is made in a single standard size. Custom dimensions are available on request.</p>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
      <p class="dm-desc__note">Measurements are approximate and handcrafted to order, so slight variation is a natural part of solid wood. Need a different size? We can tailor the dimensions to your space.</p>
    </div>

  {%- when 'delivery' -%}
    <div class="dm-desc">
      <div class="dm-desc__intro">
        <p class="dm-desc__eyebrow">Delivery &amp; refunds</p>
        <p>Every piece is handcrafted and made to order, so all sales are final. Non-returnable does not mean unsupported — if your order arrives damaged, defective, or incorrect, we will make it right.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <div>
          <h4>All sales are final</h4>
          <p>Custom, made-to-order, used, and sale items are not eligible for return. The natural variation of solid wood — grain, tone, knots, and texture — is part of its character, not a defect.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Damaged or defective on arrival</h4>
          <p>If a piece arrives damaged, defective, or different from what you ordered, you may request a refund or replacement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Report within 7 days</h4>
          <p>Contact us within 7 days of delivery with your order number and clear photos or video. Please keep all packaging and wait for written instructions before returning anything.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">4</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Refund timing</h4>
          <p>Approved refunds are issued to your original payment method, typically within 10 business days of approval.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="dm-desc__link" href="/policies/refund-policy">Read the full Return &amp; Refund Policy</a>
    </div>

  {%- when 'care' -%}
    <div class="dm-desc">
      <div class="dm-desc__intro">
        <p class="dm-desc__eyebrow">Care guide</p>
        <p>Solid wood is alive — it moves with the seasons and grows more beautiful with time. A few simple habits keep your piece stunning for generations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <div>
          <h4>The essentials</h4>
          <p>Wipe with a soft, dry or slightly damp cloth, use coasters, mats, and trivets, and keep the piece away from direct sunlight and heat sources.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <div>
          <h4>A rhythm of care</h4>
          <p>Daily: dust and wipe spills promptly. Seasonal: clean gently and re-nourish oiled finishes. Long-term: inspect occasionally and seek professional care when needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Materials &amp; finishes</h4>
          <p>Oil finish: re-oil every 6–12 months. Matte finish: clean gently and avoid waxes. Natural grain: embrace the unique markings that make each piece one of a kind.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dm-desc__item">
        <span class="dm-desc__num" aria-hidden="true">4</span>
        <div>
          <h4>What to avoid</h4>
          <p>Skip abrasive pads, silicone sprays, and harsh chemicals, and never place hot items directly on the surface — always use a trivet.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="dm-desc__link" href="/pages/care-guide">See the full Care Guide</a>
    </div>

  {%- when 'customization' -%}
    <div class="dm-desc">
      <div class="dm-desc__intro">
        <p class="dm-desc__eyebrow">Customization</p>
        <p>Have something specific in mind? Every WRYDECO piece can be tailored to you — choose your slab and finish, adjust the dimensions, or work one-on-one with our design concierge to create a piece made entirely for your space.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="dm-desc__note">Share your space, style, and timeline, and we'll guide you from first sketch to finished piece.</p>
      <a class="dm-desc__link" href="/pages/customization">Request a private consultation</a>
    </div>

  {%- else -%}
    {%- if block.settings.use_product_description -%}
      {{ product.description }}
    {%- else -%}
      {{ block.settings.content }}
    {%- endif -%}
{%- endcase -%}

{% stylesheet %}
  .dm-desc {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
  }
  .dm-desc__intro {
    padding: var(--sp-4);
    border: var(--border-width) solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-earth-brown) 6%, transparent);
  }
  /* Colours/fonts are prefixed with .dm-tabs__rte to outrank the panel's
     `.dm-tabs__rte * { color/font !important }` reset. */
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-2) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-roboto) !important;
    font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-earth-brown) !important;
  }
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__intro p,
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__item p,
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__block p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
    line-height: var(--line-height-generous);
  }
  .dm-desc__item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: var(--sp-6) 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-4);
    border-bottom: var(--border-width) solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .dm-desc__item:last-of-type {
    padding-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: 0;
  }
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__num {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: var(--sp-6);
    height: var(--sp-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-earth-brown) 10%, transparent);
    color: var(--color-earth-brown) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-roboto) !important;
    font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
  }
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__item h4,
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__block h4 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-2) !important;
  }
  .dm-desc__chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    margin-top: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--sp-1) var(--sp-3);
    border: var(--border-width) solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-earth-brown) 5%, transparent);
    color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
    font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
  }
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__note {
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--sp-3) var(--sp-4);
    border: var(--border-width) solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-earth-brown) 5%, transparent);
    color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
    font-size: var(--font-size-body-sm);
    line-height: var(--line-height-generous);
  }
  .dm-tabs__rte .dm-desc__link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--color-earth-brown) !important;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
{% endstylesheet %}
